name: MSRI-SIX-GIFYGBV-RWh-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-SIX-GIFYGBV-RWh-01" Is a six projection artwork. There are 6 gif animations of a one 3d Object which is  generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are animated in 4 layers for each color: Yellow, Green, Blue, Violet. The cells of the Red  "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. Another one group of cells linked to the same attractor points  are rotating as the white cube. Order of projection is from upper left to down right is: Left, Front, Top, Bottom, Back, Right.  Total 128 frames, 1024*1536 px canvas.
